sql1:
SELECT _id as id, name, streetaddress, latlng, postal, lic_status, citytown, lic_number
		FROM home
		WHERE record_status = %s
	 AND (  lic_status LIKE %s  OR  lic_status = %s  OR  lic_status LIKE %s  )  ORDER BY `name`
